job.title: NHM UP Community Health Officer Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 3597  Vacancies in Uttar Pradesh
job.body:
Total vacancies:2800

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Community Health Officer 

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for nurses have been published by National Health Mission for Community Health Officer vacancies in Uttar Pradesh. If you are searching for a government job in Uttar Pradesh then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Community Health Officer from 30-06-2021, and till 20-07-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Uttar Pradesh and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about the application fee

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Community Health Officer in NHM, your B.Sc. Nursing must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 30-06-2021 at 11:00 AM
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 20-07-2021 at 23:59 PM

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 35 years old. 

NHM Community Health Officer Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

How to apply for NHM UP Community Health Officer Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Community Health Officer Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of NHM and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by NHM
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
